# Approve the Coverage Matrix Edges

## Step

Walk Joel through the drafted coverage matrix's contested rows only — the routes flagged include/exclude/include-with-note (Mux asset exposure, signed upload URLs, search index fields, memory/surveys). One question per edge, recommendation first. Output: the matrix rows locked as the contract; the approved matrix graduates from draft asset to the spec the CI test table implements.

Resolved when every flagged row has an operator decision recorded and the matrix asset is marked approved.
